QUALITY REVIEW BOARD
683076 29A Establishment of Quality Review Board.-
1913482 1The Central Government shall, by notification, constitute a Quality Review Board consisting of a Chairperson and four other members.
1200962 2The Chairperson and members of the Board shall be appointed from amongst the persons of eminence having experience in the field of law, economics, business, finance or accountancy.
620784 3Two members of the Board shall be nominated by the Council and other two members shall be nominated by the Central Government.
1750322 29B Functions of Board.- The Board shall perform the following functions, namely:-
477428 ato make recommendations to the Council with regard to the quality of services provided by the members of the Institute;
589780 bto review the quality of services provided by the members of the Institute including secretarial services; and
532785 cto guide the members of the Institute to improve the quality of services and adherence to the various statutory and other regulatory requirements.
914929 29C Procedure of Board.- The Board shall meet at such time and place and follow in its meetings such procedure as may be specified. 29D. Terms and conditions of service of Chairperson and members of Board and its expenditure.-
349324 1The terms and conditions of service of the Chairperson and the members of the Board, and their allowances shall be such as may be specified.
