642915 28Insertion of new section 36A.- After section 36 of the principal Act, the following section shall be inserted, namely:- " 36A. Members, etc. to be public servants.- The Chairperson, Presiding Officer, members and other officers and employees of the Authority, Disciplinary Committee, Tribunal, Board, Board of Discipline or the Disciplinary Directorate shall be deemed to be public servants within the meaning of section 21 of the Indian Penal Code.".
